Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.27,0:00:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIDE-328
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊，這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，這個時間\N不會.謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.23,0:00:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走，怎麼了？ 很不安嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，今天什麽都沒聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽都沒？\N什麽都沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊，這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖\N你什麽都沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂今天的内容\N不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.45,0:00:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都沒告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.19,0:01:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很好\N感覺很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.39,0:01:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有型，還是那麼可愛啊\N要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個制服\N很適合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙腿真漂亮\N是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.48,0:01:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是電梯上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很突然開始拍攝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.02,0:01:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？這樣還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.69,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面？\N去上面
