Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.77,0:01:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧，什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.63,0:01:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主題就是亂交\N不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.85,0:02:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣？那麼突然嗎
